description_eng: Pull days are training days where training focus is on pulling exercises, such as rows and lat pull-downs.
description_et: Tõmmete päevad on treeningpäevad, kus fookuses on tõmbamislihastega seotud harjutused.

description_eng: Push days are training days where training focus is on pushing exercises, such as bench press and overhead press.
description_et: Tõukepäevad on treeningpäevad, kus fookuses on tõukelihased, nagu rinna- ja õlalihased

description_eng: Leg days are training days where training focus is on leg exercises, such as squats and lunges.
description_et: Jalgade päevad on treeningpäevad, kus fookuses on jalgadega seotud harjutused, nagu näiteks kükid ja etteasted.
